		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掣电树朝地面猛锤，锤点造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，形成3道冲击波，各造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，该技能可连续进行3次锤击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处在掣电树后方时，掣电树向玩家方向迅速旋转半圈，造成<span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掣电树使用藤条，一次产生3个雷棘，总计4次，雷棘锁定玩家的方位，每个雷棘造成<span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掣电树使用藤条随机召唤3道落雷，每道落雷造成<span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害，一共召唤4批。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="826" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掣电树首先在<span color="#bfbfff">冠部</span><span>形成</span><span textDecoration="underline">核心</span><span>，此时花冠呈黄色，约30s后会将其转移至</span><span color="#bfbfff">根部</span><span>，此时花冠呈紫色，交替进行。掣电树见面及核心转移至</span><span color="#bfbfff">冠部</span><span>时种下</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffe599">盈</span><span textDecoration="underline">极花蕊</span><span>，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害；转移至</span><span color="#bfbfff">根部</span><span>时种下</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#cc99ff">虚</span><span textDecoration="underline">极花蕊</span><span>，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掣电树花冠朝近处地面发射激光，来回扫两趟，均造成造成<span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害，后对准玩家喷射电激光，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="434" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">若<span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffe599">盈</span><span textDecoration="underline">极花蕊</span><span>与</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#cc99ff">虚</span><span textDecoration="underline">极花蕊</span><span>均存在于场上，则两极将相吸，产生大范围爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">300%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。两极可被元素反应破坏，但在互相吸引时则不行。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">瘫痪恢复后，掣电树在原地快速旋转一圈半，造成<span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害，旋转之前的砸地也造成</span><span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="429" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掣电树进行左砸划-右砸划-锤击三段连击，均造成<span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害，产生的震波造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
