		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#8d29b4" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8d29b4">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1164" width="442" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">盈虚花蕊：<span color="#ffacff">2雷</span><span>盾，击破可阻止掣电树施放电荷相撞。<br/>原循环核心：</span><span color="#ffacff">16雷</span><span>盾，初始位于冠部，会周期性在冠部和根部转移，击破可瘫痪掣电树18s。<br/>次循环核心：</span><span color="#ffacff">8雷</span><span>盾，为原循环核心的再生版本，以后生成的都是该种核心，击破可瘫痪掣电树18s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
